aboutpara: I am a passionate Full Stack Developer with expertise in MERN stack, Python, and Django. My journey in tech has been diverse and enriching - from working as a freelance developer to completing internships, and even contributing as a ghost writer for Supermark Agency. I have experience working with cloud services like AWS, Firebase, and Supabase, as well as databases like MongoDB. I love building scalable web applications and exploring new technologies. My experience spans across different roles and industries, giving me a unique perspective on problem-solving and project delivery.
